OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally a dry and bright
OL,6,Fstart, far eastern coasts cloudier
OL,7,Finitially. Isolated showers in the far
OL,8,Fwest from midday, spreading east
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Winds are light
OL,10,Fbut breezy along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers easing during the
OL,13,Fevening, with some breaks in the cloud
OL,14,Fdeveloping allowing temperatures to
OL,15,Ffall but remain above freezing.
OL,16,FFeeling cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
