OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FSunshine and heavy thundery
OL,6,Fshowers during the day. Clouding over
OL,7,Ffrom the west during the evening with
OL,8,Frain and strong winds arriving
OL,9,Fovernight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTuesday with windy conditions and
OL,13,Fshowers following. Wednesday breezy,
OL,14,Fbright spells and isolated showers.
OL,15,FThursday looking dry and settled with
OL,16,Flight winds. Temperatures becoming
OL,17,Fwarmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
